@startuml c4_context
!theme plain

title System Context - CodeGenerator Strategy Dispatch

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<system>> #438DD5
    FontColor<<system>> white
    BackgroundColor<<external>> #999999
    FontColor<<external>> white
    BackgroundColor<<person>> #08427B
    FontColor<<person>> white
}

rectangle "Developer / AI Agent" <<person>> as user
rectangle "CodeGenerator CLI" <<system>> as cli
rectangle "CodeGenerator.Core" <<system>> as core
rectangle "Framework Modules\n(DotNet, Angular, Flask, ...)" <<system>> as frameworks
rectangle "Target Project\n(Generated Code)" <<external>> as target

user --> cli : invokes generation
cli --> core : calls IArtifactGenerator\n& ISyntaxGenerator
core --> frameworks : dispatches to\nregistered strategies
frameworks --> target : writes generated\ncode files

note right of core
  **Strategy Dispatch Chain**
  Resolves strategies by model type,
  filters by CanHandle, sorts by
  priority, invokes best match.
end note

@enduml
